javax.servlet.Servlet
public class CometDServiceBootstrapServlet
extends Object
implements javax.servlet.Servlet

Servlet implementation to bootstrap the following CometD Service once the servlet container is ready: Internally utilizes a ServerAnnotationProcessor to resolve each services CometD dependencies and capabilities as advertised by annotations such as Session Listener

  • AgentService
  • SystemService
  • SimulationService
  • DataService
  • BeaconService
